   using Color::Blue;
   // Green still requires Color::Green
   ```

4. **Multiple Enums:**
   ```cpp
   using enum Color;
   using enum Shape;
   // Both sets of enumerators available
   ```

**When NOT to use:**
- Avoid if names conflict with variables
- Don't use at global scope (defeats scoped enum purpose)

