#### 5. Bit Manipulation Utilities (`<bit>`)

**std::bit_cast - Type-Punning:**

```cpp
#include <bit>
#include <cstdint>

// Safe type reinterpretation (replaces unsafe unions/memcpy)
float f = 3.14f;
uint32_t bits = std::bit_cast<uint32_t>(f);  // View float as uint32_t

// Convert back
